title: Fantasy Superlatives and Week 9 Must-Adds | The Dantasy Football Podcast (Ep. 333)
description:
The Ringer’s Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly offer up some “Initial Advice” after Week 8 (1:30) and recommend which players you should pick up off waivers heading into Week 9 (11:00). Then the guys give out their midseason awards to the fantasy players who have shined, flopped, and everything in between (21:30).

Tweet your fantasy football superlatives to @Danny_Heifetz and @DannyBKelly on Twitter
